  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My husband-- we both-- in the beginning, he went to work, like he worked in Israel.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But then it wasn't for him.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he-- we went with another couple.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We bought a milk bar in [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Deer Park. ?] By that time, I had already Julius.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because after all, you know, he was born the year after.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was born in August, '52.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we went into the [? milk bar ?] when he was a few months old.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it just evolved from there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then it wasn't really enough for two couples.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he started, really.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We decided that I am not going to work for the time being, that I-- because he was really-- both of the children were sick.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I mean, they were-- they did not, physically-- I mean, you know, they couldn't-- the food, the-- the reflex-- they had sort of a certain kind of a reflex, that they-- they ate something.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they didn't want to eat it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they were bringing-- you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So they were not really healthy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Physically, they were not healthy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took years, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Now, thanks God, they're as healthy as you can be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But then, they went were not.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he started to travel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he started to-- he went into small goods.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he went into small goods.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had a big clientele in the country.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the other things he was helping them too-- with interpretations of letters, with writing letters.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then he was sending me to do all kinds of things for him, you know, businesswise, and with the letters, and in various languages.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it evolved like this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We did establish a very-- again, I went-- I was the heart of this family.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
